<p>Twinning: He also posted a photo of their son Gideon Scott, nine, in a blue life preserver with Swedish Fish in his mouth like fangs, writing: 'I took a pic of a Swedish vampire!!' The professional chef later posted a pic of Gideon's twin sister Harper Grace, also nine, listening to headphones and cuddling their dog Spike in the backseat of a car, writing: 'Puppy love...'</p>

